Here's a basic .gitignore file for a Django REST Framework project:

# Django-specific files
*.sqlite*
*.db*
db.sqlite3

# Python files
*.pyc
*.pyo
__pycache__

# Test files
*.pyc
*.pyo
__pycache__
tests.py
*test*.py

# IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.DS_Store

# Build files
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Local configuration
local_settings.py

# Environment files
.env*